&lt;/div>
&lt;h2>Overview&lt;span class="hx-absolute -hx-mt-20" id="overview">&lt;/span>
&lt;a href="#overview" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;p>A plug-and-play solution to turn any &lt;strong>Raspberry Pi&lt;/strong> into a &lt;strong>full-screen media kiosk&lt;/strong> player. Automatically plays videos, PowerPoint presentations, PDFs and image slideshows from a USB stick or local storage — all rendered via &lt;strong>Chromium&lt;/strong>.&lt;/p>
&lt;p>Ideal for installations, exhibitions, digital signage or any stage use case requiring automatic media playback.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2>Features&lt;span class="hx-absolute -hx-mt-20" id="features">&lt;/span>
&lt;a href="#features" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Autoplay on boot&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Supports: video, PDF, PowerPoint (converted), image slideshows&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Load from USB stick or local storage&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Chromium in kiosk mode (full-screen, no UI)&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Simple configuration&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2>Requirements&lt;span class="hx-absolute -hx-mt-20" id="requirements">&lt;/span>
&lt;a href="#requirements" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Raspberry Pi (any recent generation)&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Raspberry Pi OS&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Chromium (included by default on Raspberry Pi OS)&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2>Links&lt;span class="hx-absolute -hx-mt-20" id="links">&lt;/span>
&lt;a href="#links" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://github.com/dewiweb/rpi-media-kiosk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub repository&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Language: HTML/Shell&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul></description></item><item><title>music-constellation</title><link>https://dewiweb.github.io/en/docs/projets/outils-sceniques/music-constellation/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://dewiweb.github.io/en/docs/projets/outils-sceniques/music-constellation/</guid><description>
&lt;div style="display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:6px;margin:1.2rem 0 1.8rem;">
&lt;a href="https://github.com/dewiweb/music-constellation" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none;">
&lt;img src="https://img.shields.io/github/stars/dewiweb/music-constellation?style=flat-square&amp;logo=github&amp;color=6366f1&amp;labelColor=1e1e2e" alt="GitHub stars" />
&lt;/a>
&lt;a href="https://github.com/dewiweb/music-constellation/commits" target="_blank" style="text-decoration:none;">
&lt;img src="https://img.shields.io/github/last-commit/dewiweb/music-constellation?style=flat-square&amp;color=10b981&amp;labelColor=1e1e2e" alt="Last commit" />
&lt;/a>
&lt;img src="https://img.shields.io/github/languages/top/dewiweb/music-constellation?style=flat-square&amp;color=f59e0b&amp;labelColor=1e1e2e" alt="true" />
&lt;/div>
&lt;h2>Overview&lt;span class="hx-absolute -hx-mt-20" id="overview">&lt;/span>
&lt;a href="#overview" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;p>A web application that represents a &lt;strong>&lt;a href="https://beets.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">beets&lt;/a>&lt;/strong> music library as an &lt;strong>interactive constellation&lt;/strong>. Each star is an album or artist, and the links between them illustrate relationships (genres, years, similarities).&lt;/p>
&lt;p>A poetic, visual way to explore your music collection.&lt;/p>
&lt;h2>Features&lt;span class="hx-absolute -hx-mt-20" id="features">&lt;/span>
&lt;a href="#features" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Connect to a beets library (via the beets web API)&lt;/li>
&lt;li>SVG/Canvas constellation graph representation&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Interactive navigation (zoom, pan, select)&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Filter by genre, decade, artist&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2>Stack&lt;span class="hx-absolute -hx-mt-20" id="stack">&lt;/span>
&lt;a href="#stack" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>TypeScript&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Visualisation: D3.js or Canvas&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Backend: beets API&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;h2>Links&lt;span class="hx-absolute -hx-mt-20" id="links">&lt;/span>
&lt;a href="#links" class="subheading-anchor" aria-label="Permalink for this section">&lt;/a>&lt;/h2>&lt;ul>
&lt;li>&lt;a href="https://github.com/dewiweb/music-constellation" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub repository&lt;/a>&lt;/li>
&lt;li>Language: TypeScript&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul></description></item><item><title>Bitfocus Companion modules</title><link>https://dewiweb.github.io/en/docs/projets/outils-sceniques/companion-modules/</link><pubDate>Mon, 01 Jan 0001 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://dewiweb.github.io/en/docs/projets/outils-sceniques/companion-modules/</guid><description>
