&lt;p>Companion module for controlling &lt;strong>Canon cameras&lt;/strong> via the legacy HTTP network API. Allows driving compatible Canon cameras from a Stream Deck.&lt;/p>
&lt;ul>
&lt;li>Language: JavaScript · Protocol: HTTP&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;hr>
